you stop and think,

00:10:57.720 --> 00:11:01.060
and you go, hang on, why
does that happen over there,

00:11:01.060 --> 00:11:04.470
and why don't we have that
here, that you start to think,

00:11:04.470 --> 00:11:06.020
what's going on?

00:11:06.020 --> 00:11:08.570
And I guess the
consequence of it

00:11:08.570 --> 00:11:11.010
being, maybe, not
as easy to give pets

