pet that goes to your knee,

00:37:23.530 --> 00:37:25.690
you can't have the apartment.

00:37:25.690 --> 00:37:27.891
CHRIS BROWN: I'm quite
tall, I could [INAUDIBLE].

00:37:27.891 --> 00:37:28.390
[LAUGHTER]

00:37:28.390 --> 00:37:29.015
AUDIENCE: Yeah.

00:37:29.015 --> 00:37:30.312
You'd be fine.

00:37:30.312 --> 00:37:32.520
But yeah, my really good
friend had a Doberman.

00:37:32.520 --> 00:37:35.380
Obviously, she couldn't
get the apartment.

00:37:35.380 --> 00:37:38.130
So is that something
as well, that-- like,

00:37:38.130 --> 00:37:42.830
I only had a cat in France, and
cats are no problem for pets

00:37:42.830 --> 00:37:43.332
in France.

00:37:43.332 --> 00:37:45.540
But is that something that
you're looking at as well,

00:37:45.540 --> 00:37:48.020
to work with the governments
