00:49:30.670 --> 00:49:32.210
Particularly, in
Sydney-- the fact

00:49:32.210 --> 00:49:36.250
that it's such an unfriendly
city for dogs in particular.

00:49:36.250 --> 00:49:37.960
Has it always been like that?

00:49:37.960 --> 00:49:39.720
What was the factor?

00:49:39.720 --> 00:49:42.070
Was there an event
or a chain of events

00:49:42.070 --> 00:49:45.420
that triggered this sort of
regulations against dogs,

00:49:45.420 --> 00:49:48.710
which don't seem to be
based on any actual facts,

00:49:48.710 --> 00:49:50.328
as you mentioned?

00:49:50.328 --> 00:49:51.529
CHRIS BROWN: Yeah.

00:49:51.529 --> 00:49:53.070
There's not really
an exact, sort of,

00:49:53.070 --> 00:49:54.870
moment where it all changed.

00:49:54.870 --> 00:50:00.190
Generally, through the '60s,
'70s, and probably early '80s,

00:50:00.190 --> 00:50:01.910
we were fairly
relaxed, but we didn't

00:50:01.910 --> 00:50:06.500
have a lot of
policy around where

00:50:06.500 --> 00:50:09.120
we sat around our regulations.

00:50:09.120 --> 00:50:12.910
But once we actually became
more, I guess, litigious,

00:50:12.910 --> 00:50:17.550
and more keen to regulate,
when we regulated,

00:50:17.550 --> 00:50:21.140
we went, I guess,
probably above and beyond,

00:50:21.140 --> 00:50:23.820
where a lot of those
other nations have.

00:50:23.820 --> 00:50:27.150
So we've never been one of
the most pet-friendly nations

00:50:27.150 --> 00:50:30.480
in the world, when it
comes to regulations.

00:50:30.480 --> 00:50:34.710
And certainly over the
last 10 or 15 years,

00:50:34.710 --> 00:50:38.340
we haven't necessarily
progressed and caught up

00:50:38.340 --> 00:50:41.560
with some of the
deregulation that's happening

00:50:41.560 --> 00:50:43.790
in some of the other countries.

00:50:43.790 --> 00:50:47.220
So we were always behind, but
I think over the last 15 years

00:50:47.220 --> 00:50:50.590
or so, we've got further
behind, because we've actually

00:50:50.590 --> 00:50:52.950
regulated more heavily, while
a lot of other countries

00:50:52.950 --> 00:50:55.150
have become a little
bit more relaxed.

00:50:55.150 --> 00:50:57.150
