00:50:59.470 --> 00:51:00.920
What other sort
of things are you

00:51:00.920 --> 00:51:01.950
seeing that's
different in Sydney,

00:51:01.950 --> 00:51:02.915
compared to the
rest of Australia?

00:51:02.915 --> 00:51:03.665
CHRIS BROWN: Yeah.

00:51:03.665 --> 00:51:07.410
It's to do with-- accessibility
of rental properties

00:51:07.410 --> 00:51:08.780
is quite low.

00:51:08.780 --> 00:51:11.320
And I know, just anecdotally
through my friends,

00:51:11.320 --> 00:51:14.380
that they really struggle
to find rental properties.

00:51:14.380 --> 00:51:17.000
Lack of exercise
areas is a huge one.

00:51:17.000 --> 00:51:19.620
So it's very hard
to find a dog beach

00:51:19.620 --> 00:51:24.290
to take your dog in Sydney,
whereas in Melbourne,

00:51:24.290 --> 00:51:27.910
for example, there is quite
a few that you can go to.

00:51:27.910 --> 00:51:30.810
But also, it comes
down to policy

00:51:30.810 --> 00:51:33.790
and looking to be
positive with our policy.

00:51:33.790 --> 00:51:39.910
We tend to over-regulate,
fine-- we're very

00:51:39.910 --> 00:51:41.410
strict with our registration.

00:51:41.410 --> 00:51:44.000
So it's almost like
there's a negative tone

00:51:44.000 --> 00:51:47.690
to our policy-making, whereas
in some of the other states,

00:51:47.690 --> 00:51:50.800
in meeting with the other
states-- Victoria, for example,

00:51:50.800 --> 00:51:54.660
is very positive when it
comes to their puppy-farming

00:51:54.660 --> 00:51:55.230
legislation.

00:51:55.230 --> 00:51:59.270
They're very positive when it
comes to their registration

00:51:59.270 --> 00:52:02.670
policies for pets, and reward
you for doing the right thing.

00:52:02.670 --> 00:52:06.810
South Australia are
looking at a situation

00:52:06.810 --> 00:52:09.520
where you'll get
discounted registration

00:52:09.520 --> 00:52:13.770
fees if you can show your
dog's gone to training.

00:52:13.770 --> 00:52:15.710
And I think that's a
much better way to be,

00:52:15.710 --> 00:52:18.330
if you can actually give a
little bit to actually get

00:52:18.330 --> 00:52:21.535
something back in return, as
opposed to, do it this way

00:52:21.535 --> 00:52:23.910
or you're going to be fined,
which I think has often been

00:52:23.910 --> 00:52:25.420
